To quantify the surfactant effect on the blading process, capillary number (Ca) is perhaps a good metric, which is the dimensionless ratio of viscous force (fvis) to surface tension (fsur) [39–42]:1Ca=fvisfsur=μvγ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
